Iberdrola Is a Candidate to Buy RWE’s U.K. Unit, Expansion Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-07-05T05:38:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-05/iberdrola-is-a-candidate-to-buy-rwe-s-u-k-unit-expansion-says.html
Iberdrola SA (IBE)  is in the running to
purchase  RWE AG (RWE) ’s Npower unit in the U.K.,  Expansion  reported,
citing unidentified analysts in London.  The Spanish company would have the fewest difficulties
getting approval from competition authorities if it bought the
unit, which is valued at 5.5 billion euros ($8 billion), the
newspaper added.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Sills at 
 bsills@bloomberg.net  